d-michael-levin-and-lex-fridman</guid></item><item><title>铁锈到铁的循环可能会开启可再生能源的长期储存</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/rust-to-iron-cycle-may-unlock-long-term-storage-for-renewable-energy</link><description>未来，铁可能被用作化学储能材料，从长远来看可以提供大量的可再生能源。铁粉在碳中性的循环过程中燃烧，然后利用能量输入恢复到其原始状态。卡尔斯鲁厄理工学院 (KIT) 的科学家率先进行了广泛的研究，以评估该技术的发电潜力。他们的研究结果表明，铁虽然不能取代氢，但可以在气候中性能源系统中有效地补充氢。研究结果是&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/rust-to-iron-cycle-may-unlock-long-term-storage-for-renewable-energy.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 13:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/rust-to-iron-cycle-may-unlock-long-term-storage-for-renewable-energy</guid></item><item><title>乔治·帕里西 (Giorgio Parisi) 的《八哥飞翔》</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/in-a-flight-of-starlings-by-giorgio-parisi</link><description>来自 2021 年诺贝尔物理学奖获得者的开创性科学实践的启发性个人之旅。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/in-a-flight-of-starlings-by-giorgio-parisi2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 13:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/in-a-flight-of-starlings-by-giorgio-parisi</guid></item><item><title>“CORLEO”概念亮相</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/corleo-concept-unveiled</link><description>后腿单元可以独立于前腿单元上下摆动，使其能够吸收行走和跑步时的震动。另外，在爬台阶时，骑手可以保持避免向上看的姿势，更容易查看前方的路况。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/corleo-concept-unveiled.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:46:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/corleo-concept-unveiled</guid></item><item><title>像沙丘一样宏伟......但很少有人见过它</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/as-grand-as-dune-yet-few-have-seen-it</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:31:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/as-grand-as-dune-yet-few-have-seen-it</guid></item><item><title>蘑菇可以降低低密度脂蛋白吗？ 53-测试分析</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/can-mushrooms-reduce-ldl-53-test-analysis</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/can-mushrooms-reduce-ldl-53-test-analysis</guid></item><item><title>打破规则的章鱼如何改写智力的进化</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/how-the-rule-breaking-octopus-is-rewriting-the-evolution-of-intelligence</link><description>头足类动物是孤独的动物，但它们也很聪明&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-the-rule-breaking-octopus-is-rewriting-the-evolution-of-intelligence.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/how-the-rule-breaking-octopus-is-rewriting-the-evolution-of-intelligence</guid></item><item><title>环状肽围绕疾病靶标运行</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/circular-peptides-run-rings-around-disease-targets</link><description>一种新型药物发现平台暗示，具有类似变色龙特性的非常规候选化合物可能会攻击以前“无法成药”的疾病目标。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/circular-peptides-run-rings-around-disease-targets.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 11:46:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/circular-peptides-run-rings-around-disease-targets</guid></item></channel></rss>